
Project Outline
- Features
    - Add Folder(s) 
        - folder tile change to dynamic - user imput (done)
    - Edit Folders (s) (done)
    - Remove Folder(s) - (done)
    - Identify which folder the items are being add/edit/etc to.(done)
    - Add new items to folder (done)
    - Remove items within folder (done)
    - List items within folder (done)
    - Edit items within folder (done)
    - Search for item in folder (done)
    - Search for item using Title (done)
    
   
- Properties 
    - Folder Manager
        - Folders[]
    - Folder
        - ID
        - Title
        - Items[]
    - Item(s)
        - ID
        - Title

- FrontEnd
    - Blank screen
    - Edit Mode
    - Add button (auto saves)
    - Delete button

- Backend
    - Api server (look up api servers)
        - FastAPI / Django (done)
        - Api endpoints (RESTful - RESTAPI)
            - /folders (done)
                - GET (list all folders)
                - POST (add new folder) 
            - /folders/{folder_id} (done)
                - GET (get specific folder detail
                - PUT (update folder details)
                - DELETE (remove folder)
            - /folders/{folder_id}/items (done)
                - GET (list all items in a folder)
                - POST (add new item to a folder)
            - /folders/{folder_id}/items/{item_id}
                - GET (get specific item details)
                - PUT (update item details)
                - DELETE (remove item from folder)
    - Handle hard & soft deletes 
    - Database
        - Postgress
    - Docker (done)
    - https://docs.astral.sh/uv/#python-versions (done)
    - https://docs.astral.sh/uv/guides/scripts/#running-a-script-without-dependencies (done)

